\section{SUMMARY}
\label{sec:orgb8cfb61}

Bruce is a BSc (Math, Operational Research) graduate with further studies in Financial engineering and business reporting, through ASSA. 
Bruce has acted as his own investment manager since 2017 where he has developed a growing knowledge of global investment opportunities.
Bruce's entreprenarial flare led him to become involved in an ice cream wholesaler startup in Cape Town where he put his knowledge of modelling to use to anticipate business profitability and cash flow. 

Bruce is planning to relocate to the United Kingdom in December at his own cost. Bruce has ancestral rights to a work visa.

